za|Almanza]] || '''[[Mike Morgan (baseball)|Morgan]]''' || [[Antonio Alfonseca|Alfonseca]] (31) || [[Pro Player Stadium]] || 16,770 || 58&ndash;47 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/FLO/FLO200007300.shtml]\n|}</div></div>\n|-\n|<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n<div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"background:#006265; color:#fff; text-align:center;\"><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">August (0&ndash;0) (Home: 0&ndash;0; Road: 0&ndash;0)</span></div>\n<div class=\"NavContent\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:3%;\"| #\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:11%;\"| Date\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:11%;\"| Opponent\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:9%;\"| Score\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:14%;\"| Win\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:13%;\"| Loss\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:13%;\"| Save\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:7%;\"| Stadium\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:5%;\"| Attendance\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:5%;\"| Record\n!  style=\"background:#ddf; width:5%;\"| Report\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#fbb;\"\n| 106 || August 1 || [[2000 Atlanta Braves season|Braves]] || 2&ndash;4 || [[Kevin Millwood|Millwood]] || '''[[Greg Swindell|Swindell]]''' || [[Mike Remlinger|Remlinger]] || [[Bank One Ballpark]] || 35,138 || 58&ndash;48 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI200008010.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 107 || August 2 || [[2000 Atlanta Braves season|Braves]] || 2&ndash;0 || '''[[Curt Schilling|Schilling]]''' || [[Greg Maddux|Maddux]] || ''None'' || [[Bank One Ballpark]] || 40,643 || 59&ndash;48 || [https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ARI/ARI200008020.shtml]\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#bfb;\"\n| 108 || August 3 || [[2000 Atlanta Braves season|Braves]] || 8&ndash;4 || '''[[Brian Anderson (pitcher)|Anderson]]''' || [[Andy Ashby|Ashby]] || ''None'' || [[Bank One Ballpark]] || 35,441 || 60&ndash;48 || [h